      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"اَلْهَدِيَّةُ ثَلاَثٌ هَدِيَّةُ مُكَافَأَةٍ وَ هَدِيَّةُ مُصَانَعَةٍ وَ هَدِيَّةٌ لِلَّهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4077 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Gifts are of three types: a gift given in reciprocation, a gift given to seek favor, and a gift given for the sake of Allah (swt), the Almighty and Glorious.\""
        ]
      }
    },
